Longtime I have been waiting for the coming of my dear;

Longtime I have been waiting for the coming of my dear.

Sometimes I am uneasy and troubled in my mind.

Sometimes I think I’ll go to my love and tell to him my mind;

Sometimes I think I’ll go to my love and tell to him my mind.

