items.notes:
The Seven Wonders

[trad. arr. Prior / Tabor]

Maddy Prior, June Tabor, vocals;

Tony Hall, melodeon;

Martin Carthy, guitars;

Andy Irvine, hurdy-gurdy;

Johnny Moynihan, bouzouki;

Danny Thompson, bass;

John Gillaspie, bombard

This song from the Alps of Wales was collected from Mick Tems of Pontardawe.

It was sung by Maddy Prior and June Tabor on their album

Silly Sisters .

